name: Cactus Yeehaw
description:
Description

Help Cactus Yeehaw, savior of the desert, bring the stranded cowboy back to town! Reach a score of 20,000 points to win!

Controls

WASD/Arrow Keys

Good Items

  • Aloe bottles
  • Bags of fertilizer
  • Water bottles

Bad Items
